Replaces: gnome-control-center (<< 1:2.14.1-1)
Description: Utility library for getting window manager settings (headers)
 This package contains the libwindow-settings library header files.

Package: libgnome-settings-daemon-dev
Architecture: all
Section: libdevel
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         capplets-data (>= ${gnome:Version}),
         capplets-data (<< ${gnome:NextVersion})
Description: Utility library for accessing g-s-d over DBUS (headers)
 This package contains the header files to use interoperate with
 gnome-settings-daemon through a DBus service.
